Interface GTNetMessageAttemptJpaRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<GTNetMessageAttempt>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>
public interface GTNetMessageAttemptJpaRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<GTNetMessageAttempt,Integer>
Repository for managing GTNetMessageAttempt entities that track per-target delivery status for future-oriented broadcast messages.

This repository provides methods for:

  • Finding pending deliveries (hasSend = false) by message or target
  • Finding and deleting specific message-target combinations
  • Querying pending future-oriented messages for the delivery task
